{"word":"H7270 - רָגַל - râgal - raw-gal' - Backbite","slug":"H7270","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָגַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râgal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-gal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Backbite"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D2;&#x05DC; - ra&#x0302;gal</b> - <i>raw-gal'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>walk</i> along; but only in specific applications, to <i>reconnoitre</i>, to <i>be a tale bearer</i> (that is, slander); also (as denominative from <a href=\"#/H7272\">H7272</a>) to <i>lead about: - </i>backbite, search, slander, (e-) spy (out), teach to go, view."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4772\">H4772</a>, <a href=\"#/H7272\">H7272</a>, <a href=\"#/H7273\">H7273</a>, <a href=\"#/H7274\">H7274</a>, <a href=\"#/H8637\">H8637</a>"}]}